==军事和政府运作==
弗雷斯诺机场是{{link-en|加利福尼亚空军国民警卫队|California Air National Guard}}的{{link-en|第144战斗机联队|144th Fighter Wing}}之驻地。<ref>{{cite web | author= | title=Fresno Air National Guard Base | url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/facility/fresno.htm | work=Global Security | year=2005 | accessdate=2011-03-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110128045453/http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/facility/fresno.htm | archive-date=2011-01-28 | dead-url=no }}</ref>加利福尼亚陆军国民警卫队亦在此设有一个航空分类维修活动站（{{lang-en|Aviation Classification Repair Activity Depot}}，AVCRAD）。<ref name="Master Plan Ch 2" />这一维修活动站为陆军飞机提供高水平的维护和维修，其管辖范围覆盖了美国西部的15个州。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Van Dyke|first1=Col. Mark|title=1106th TASMG Overview Presentation|url=http://www.ncfa.ncr.gov/sites/default/files/1106%20TASMG%20NCFA%20Brief.pdf|publisher=National Commission on the Future of the Army|accessdate=2018-03-13|date=2015-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180314043524/http://www.ncfa.ncr.gov/sites/default/files/1106%20TASMG%20NCFA%20Brief.pdf|archive-date=2018-03-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

[[美国国家森林局|美国国家森林局]]和{{link-en|加利福尼亚林业和消防部|California Department of Forestry and Fire Protection}}共同在此运作一座以灭火飞机扑救森林火灾的{{link-en|弗雷斯诺空中消防基地|Fresno Air Attack Base|空中消防基地}}。<ref>{{cite web|title=Fresno Air Attack Base factsheet|url=http://www.calfire.ca.gov/about/downloads/air_attack_bases/Fresno.pdf|publisher=California Department of Forestry|accessdate=2018-03-13|date=January 2005|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508133820/http://calfire.ca.gov/about/downloads/air_attack_bases/Fresno.pdf|archive-date=2018-05-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

其他的政府及军事运营者包括{{link-en|加利福尼亚陆军国民警卫队|California Army National Guard}}、[[加利福尼亚州公路巡警|加利福尼亚州公路巡警]]、{{link-en|弗雷斯诺县警长办公室|Fresno County Sheriff's Office}}与{{link-en|弗雷斯诺警察局|Fresno Police Department}}。

==地面交通==

===公路===
机场距离{{link-en|180号加利福尼亚州州道|California State Route 180|180号加州州道}}约{{convert|1|mile|km}}远，皮奇大道（{{lang-en|Peach Avenue}}）联通高速公路与机场。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hostetter|first1=George|title=Fresno’s Peach Avenue gets long-sought widening|url=http://www.fresnobee.com/news/local/article19528746.html|accessdate=2018-04-16|work=[[The_Fresno_Bee|The Fresno Bee]]|date=2014-12-23|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180417023843/http://www.fresnobee.com/news/local/article19528746.html|archive-date=2018-04-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>180号加州州道联通到弗雷斯诺区域其他所有的高速公路：{{link-en|41号加利福尼亚州州道|California State Route 41|41号加州州道}}、[[99号加利福尼亚州州道|99号加州州道]]和{{link-en|168号加利福尼亚州州道|California State Route 168|168号加州州道}}。<ref name="CAHighways 180">{{cite web|title=State Route 180|url=https://cahighways.org/177-184.html#180|website=California Highways|accessdate=2018-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180417023257/https://cahighways.org/177-184.html#180|archive-date=2018-04-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>41号加州州道联通约塞米蒂国家公园，美洲杉国家公园和国王峡谷国家公园可通过180号加州州道到达。<ref>{{cite web|title=Driving Directions - Yosemite National Park|url=https://www.nps.gov/yose/planyourvisit/driving.htm|publisher=National Park Service|language=en|access-date=2019-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412232931/https://www.nps.gov/yose/planyourvisit/driving.htm|archive-date=2019-04-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Driving Directions - Sequoia & Kings Canyon National Parks|url=https://www.nps.gov/seki/planyourvisit/directions.htm|publisher=National Park Service|language=en|access-date=2019-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412232929/https://www.nps.gov/seki/planyourvisit/directions.htm|archive-date=2019-04-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>

